text: "Fed Up" is the a song by DJ Khaled. It was released on March 2, 2010. It became his first single from his album Victory (2010). The song features Usher, Young Jeezy, Rick Ross and Drake. ==Charts== Chart (2009-2010) Peak Position US Bubbling Under Hot 100 Singles (Billboard) 8 US Hot R&B;/Hip-Hop Songs (Billboard) 45 US Rap Songs (Billboard) 22 Category:2009 songs Category:Drake (musician) songs Category:Lil Wayne songs Category:Usher songs
